{{> base}}

<div>
  <h2>Subscription Cancellation Confirmation</h2>
  <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
  <p>We're sorry to see you go. Your subscription to the {{plan}} plan has been canceled.</p>

  <h3>Cancellation Details:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Plan: {{plan}}</li>
    <li>Access Until: {{formatDate endDate}}</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Your subscription will remain active until {{formatDate endDate}}. During this time, you can:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Continue using all features of your current plan</li>
    <li>Export your data</li>
    <li>Download any reports or analytics</li>
  </ul>

  <p>If you change your mind, you can reactivate your subscription at any time before {{formatDate endDate}}.</p>

  <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Reactivate Subscription</a>

  <p>We value your feedback. If you'd like to share why you're leaving, please take a moment to complete our exit survey.</p>

  <a href="{{feedbackUrl}}" class="button">Provide Feedback</a>

  <p>Thank you for being a valued customer. We hope to serve you again in the future.</p>

  <p>Best regards,<br>The Blockchain Voting System Team</p>
</div> 